==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|tu}}

===Etymology===
Proto-Finno-Permic ''*tule''.  Cognates include Estonian [[tuul]]. 

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]] /tuːli/
*[[w:X-SAMPA|X-SAMPA]] /tu:li/

===Noun===
'''tuuli'''

#[[wind]]
#:''tuuli puhaltaa pohjoisesta'' (wind blows from the north)
#[[mood]] (of mind)
#:''hän on hyvällä tuulella'' (she is in a good mood)

===Verb from===
'''tuuli'''

#[[third person]] [[singular]] [[imperfect]] [[indicative]] of [[tuulla]] (to [[blow]])
#:''hetki sitten tuuli kovaa'' (a moment ago the wind blew hard)

